query:
UPDATE
                http_trigger
            SET
                route_path = $1,
                route_path_key = $2,
                workspaced_route = $3,
                wrap_body = $4,
                raw_string = $5,
                authentication_resource_path = $6,
                script_path = $7,
                path = $8,
                is_flow = $9,
                mode = $10,
                http_method = $11,
                static_asset_config = $12,
                edited_by = $13,
                email = $14,
                request_type = $15,
                authentication_method = $16,
                summary = $17,
                description = $18,
                edited_at = now(),
                is_static_website = $19,
                error_handler_path = $20,
                error_handler_args = $21,
                retry = $22
            WHERE
                workspace_id = $23 AND
                path = $24
